import React from "react";
import styled from "styled-components";

const StyledIcon = styled.svg`
  width: 40px;

  ${media.up.medium`
  width: 70px;
`};
`;

const HealthyHome = ({ fill }) => (
  <StyledIcon
    fill={fill}
    viewBox="0 0 90 90"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    role="img"
    aria-labelledby="healthy-home-title"
  >
    <title id="healthy-home-title">Healthy Home icon</title>
    <path fill="#C4C4C4" d="M0 0h90v90H0z" />
    <path fill="#F7F0DA" d="M24 34h42v41H24z" />
    <path fill="#823333" d="M58 14h6v20h-6z" />
    <path
      d="M68 6.5a3.5 3.5 0 11-7 0 3.5 3.5 0 017 0zM64 12.5a3.5 3.5 0 11-7 0 3.5 3.5 0 017 0z"
      fill="#3F4541"
      fill-opacity=".3"
    />
    <path
      d="M64 8.5a3.5 3.5 0 11-7 0 3.5 3.5 0 017 0z"
      fill="#3F4541"
      fill-opacity=".3"
    />
    <path
      d="M43.463 10.847a2 2 0 013.074 0l22.58 27.123c1.084 1.303.158 3.28-1.537 3.28H22.42c-1.695 0-2.621-1.977-1.537-3.28l22.58-27.123z"
      fill="#0057FF"
    />
    <path fill="#5C4300" d="M39 57h12v18H39z" />
    <path fill="#0057FF" d="M28 57h8v8h-8zM54 57h8v8h-8z" />
  </StyledIcon>
);

export default HealthyHome;
